#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:44
msgid "Text or Keyboard Conventions"
msgstr "Konvencije za tekst ili tastaturu"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:46
msgid ""
"This manual also includes styles related to text, keyboard commands and "
"coding to indicate different entities, such as classes or methods. These "
"styles do not correspond to the actual appearance of any text or coding "
"within QGIS."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj priručnik takođe uključuje stilove povezane sa tekstom, komandama "
"tastature i kodiranjem radi označavanja različitih entiteta, kao što su "
"klase ili metode. Ovi stilovi ne odgovaraju stvarnom izgledu bilo kog teksta"
" ili kodiranja unutar QGIS-a."

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:53
msgid "Hyperlinks: https://qgis.org"
msgstr "Hiperlinkovi: https://qgis.org"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:54
msgid ""
"Keystroke Combinations: Press :kbd:`Ctrl+B`, meaning press and hold the Ctrl"
" key and then press the B key."
msgstr ""
"Kombinacije tastera: Pritisnite :kbd:`Ctrl+B`, što znači pritisnite i držite"
" taster Ctrl, a zatim pritisnite taster B."

