#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:66
msgid "Lines of code are indicated by a fixed-width font:"
msgstr "Linije koda označene su fontom fiksne širine:"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:74
msgid "Platform-specific instructions"
msgstr "Instrukcije specifične za platformu"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:76
msgid ""
"GUI sequences and small amounts of text may be formatted inline: Click |nix|"
" |win| :menuselection:`File` |osx| :menuselection:`QGIS --> Quit to close "
"QGIS`. This indicates that on Linux, Unix and Windows platforms, you should "
"click the File menu first, then Quit, while on macOS platforms, you should "
"click the QGIS menu first, then Quit."
msgstr ""
"Sekvence grafičkog interfejsa i male količine teksta mogu se formatirati "
"ugrađeno: Kliknite |nix| |win| :menuselection:`Datoteka` |osx| "
":menuselection:`QGIS --> Izađi za zatvaranje QGIS-a`. Ovo označava da na "
"Linux, Unix i Windows platformama prvo treba da kliknete na meni Datoteka, "
"zatim Izađi, dok na macOS platformama prvo treba da kliknete na meni QGIS, "
"zatim Izađi."

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:110
msgid "nix"
msgstr "nix"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:124
msgid "win"
msgstr "win"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:112
msgid "osx"
msgstr "osx"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:82
msgid "Larger amounts of text may be formatted as a list:"
msgstr "Veće količine teksta mogu se formatirati kao lista:"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:84
msgid "|nix| Do this"
msgstr "|nix| Uradite ovo"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:85
msgid "|win| Do that"
msgstr "|win| Uradite ono"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:86
msgid "|osx| Or do that"
msgstr "|osx| Ili uradite ono"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:88
msgid "or as paragraphs:"
msgstr "ili kao pasusi:"

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:90
msgid ""
"|nix| |osx| Do this and this and this. Then do this and this and this, and "
"this and this and this, and this and this and this."
msgstr ""
"|nix| |osx| Uradite ovo i ovo i ovo. Zatim uradite ovo i ovo i ovo, i ovo i "
"ovo i ovo, i ovo i ovo i ovo."

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:93
msgid ""
"|win| Do that. Then do that and that and that, and that and that and that, "
"and that and that and that, and that and that."
msgstr ""
"|win| Uradite ono. Zatim uradite ono i ono i ono, i ono i ono i ono, i ono i"
" ono i ono, i ono i ono."

#: ../../docs/about/conventions.rst:96
msgid ""
"Screenshots that appear throughout the user guide have been created on "
"different platforms."
msgstr ""
"Snimci ekrana koji se pojavljuju kroz korisnički vodič napravljeni su na "
"različitim platformama."
